      A TikTok
   =20
 =20
Here=E2=80=99s a TikTok dance video=C2=A0about how Vanguard and BlackRock o=
wn all the companies? It=E2=80=99s =E2=80=A6=C2=A0not =E2=80=A6=C2=A0right?=
 =E2=80=A6=C2=A0or =E2=80=A6=C2=A0good? =E2=80=A6=C2=A0but it is =E2=80=A6=
=C2=A0a TikTok dance video about how Vanguard and BlackRock own all the com=
panies? This is an idea that we  talk about from  time to  time around here=
, and that I like to think I played some role in popularizing, though now o=
f course I regret all of my choices. I cannot recommend this video, but I d=
o feel obligated to mention it.=C2=A0
